{"prompt": "Design a modern website for a bespoke tailoring service. The aesthetic should incorporate a deep teal green.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Artisan Tailors</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #004d40; /* Deep teal green */\n            --secondary-color: #80a19e; /* Muted, lighter teal */\n            --accent-color: #f5f5f5; /* Off-white for contrast */\n            --text-color: #333333;\n            --heading-font: 'Playfair Display', serif;\n            --body-font: 'Lato', sans-serif;\n        }\n\n        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Lato:wght@300;400;700&family=Playfair+Display:wght@700&display=swap');\n\n        body {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-family: var(--body-font);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            background-color: var(--accent-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            scroll-behavior: smooth;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 90%;\n            max-width: 1200px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            padding: 40px 0;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-family: var(--heading-font);\n            font-size: 2.8em;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n\n        header p {\n            margin-top: 5px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            font-weight: 300;\n        }\n\n        nav {\n            text-align: center;\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            padding: 15px 0;\n        }\n\n        nav ul {\n            list-style: none;\n            padding: 0;\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n\n        nav ul li {\n            display: inline;\n            margin: 0 20px;\n        }\n\n        nav ul li a {\n            text-decoration: none;\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n            font-weight: 700;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        nav ul li a:hover {\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        section {\n            padding: 60px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        section h2 {\n            font-family: var(--heading-font);\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n\n        #hero {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n            background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0, 77, 64, 0.7), rgba(0, 77, 64, 0.7)), url('placeholder-tailor.jpg'); /* Replace with actual image */\n            background-size: cover;\n            background-position: center;\n            height: 60vh;\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            flex-direction: column;\n        }\n\n        #hero h2 {\n            font-size: 3.5em;\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);\n        }\n\n        #hero p {\n            font-size: 1.4em;\n            font-weight: 300;\n            max-width: 700px;\n            text-shadow: 1px 1px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);\n        }\n\n        #services .service-item {\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n        }\n\n        #services .service-item h3 {\n            font-family: var(--heading-font);\n            font-size: 1.8em;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n        }\n\n        #services .service-item p {\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            max-width: 600px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n        }\n\n        #gallery {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        #gallery h2 {\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        .gallery-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));\n            gap: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .gallery-item img {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 300px;\n            object-fit: cover;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .gallery-item img:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);\n        }\n\n        #about {\n            background-color: var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        #contact {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        #contact h2 {\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        #contact form {\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            align-items: center;\n            gap: 15px;\n            max-width: 600px;\n            margin: 30px auto 0 auto;\n        }\n\n        #contact form input,\n        #contact form textarea {\n            width: 100%;\n            padding: 12px;\n            border: 1px solid var(--primary-color);\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-size: 1em;\n            font-family: var(--body-font);\n            box-sizing: border-box; /* Include padding and border in the element's total width and height */\n        }\n\n        #contact form textarea {\n            min-height: 150px;\n            resize: vertical;\n        }\n\n        #contact form button {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;\n            font-weight: 700;\n        }\n\n        #contact form button:hover {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            transform: translateY(-2px);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px 0;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <h1>Artisan Tailors</h1>\n        <p>Crafting Elegance, One Stitch at a Time</p>\n    </header>\n\n    <nav>\n        <ul>\n            <li><a href=\"#hero\">Home</a></li>\n            <li><a href=\"#services\">Services</a></li>\n            <li><a href=\"#gallery\">Gallery</a></li>\n            <li><a href=\"#about\">About Us</a></li>\n            <li><a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a></li>\n        </ul>\n    </nav>\n\n    <section id=\"hero\">\n        <h2>Experience Bespoke Perfection</h2>\n        <p>Discover the unparalleled luxury of custom-made garments, meticulously crafted to your exact specifications.</p>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"services\" class=\"container\">\n        <h2>Our Craftsmanship</h2>\n        <div class=\"service-item\">\n            <h3>Custom Suits</h3>\n            <p>From business essentials to formal wear, we create suits that fit impeccably and reflect your personal style.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"service-item\">\n            <h3>Tailored Shirts</h3>\n            <p>Experience the comfort and sophistication of shirts made to measure, with a perfect fit guaranteed.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"service-item\">\n            <h3>Alterations & Repairs</h3>\n            <p>Expertise in refining existing garments to achieve the perfect silhouette and longevity.</p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"gallery\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Gallery of Style</h2>\n            <div class=\"gallery-grid\">\n                <div class=\"gallery-item\"><img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x300/004d40/ffffff?text=Suit+1\" alt=\"Custom suit example 1\"></div>\n                <div class=\"gallery-item\"><img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x300/004d40/ffffff?text=Shirt+1\" alt=\"Tailored shirt example 1\"></div>\n                <div class=\"gallery-item\"><img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x300/004d40/ffffff?text=Suit+2\" alt=\"Custom suit example 2\"></div>\n                <div class=\"gallery-item\"><img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x300/004d40/ffffff?text=Detail+1\" alt=\"Tailoring detail\"></div>\n                <div class=\"gallery-item\"><img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x300/004d40/ffffff?text=Suit+3\" alt=\"Custom suit example 3\"></div>\n                <div class=\"gallery-item\"><img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x300/004d40/ffffff?text=Shirt+2\" alt=\"Tailored shirt example 2\"></div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"about\" class=\"container\">\n        <h2>About Artisan Tailors</h2>\n        <p>Founded on a passion for traditional tailoring techniques and a commitment to modern aesthetics, Artisan Tailors offers a truly bespoke experience. Our skilled artisans combine quality fabrics with precision craftsmanship to create garments that are as unique as you are. We believe in the art of dressing well and are dedicated to helping you achieve your sartorial goals.</p>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"contact\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Get In Touch</h2>\n            <p>Schedule your consultation today and let us craft your perfect garment.</p>\n            <form action=\"#\" method=\"post\">\n                <input type=\"text\" name=\"name\" placeholder=\"Your Name\" required>\n                <input type=\"email\" name=\"email\" placeholder=\"Your Email\" required>\n                <textarea name=\"message\" placeholder=\"Your Message\" required></textarea>\n                <button type=\"submit\">Book Consultation</button>\n            </form>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Artisan Tailors. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        // Optional: Add smooth scrolling for navigation links\n        document.querySelectorAll('nav a[href^=\"#\"]').forEach(anchor => {\n            anchor.addEventListener('click', function (e) {\n                e.preventDefault();\n                document.querySelector(this.getAttribute('href')).scrollIntoView({\n                    behavior: 'smooth'\n                });\n            });\n        });\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>\n"}